export const isSsoProfile = (arg) => arg &&
    (typeof arg.sso_start_url === "string" ||
        typeof arg.sso_account_id === "string" ||
        typeof arg.sso_session === "string" ||
        typeof arg.sso_region === "string" ||
        typeof arg.sso_role_name === "string");
